text: Repeat customer but 1st time ordering MEE GORENG! I am a chilli padi lover, unfortunately, this MEE GORENG is a BIG Challenge! All of it is sambal! Its spicy is unspeakable. All sambal and stomach is feeling HOT right now!. Oh dear.

I usually buy from the other stalls but one day, my neighbor said this stall is nice and always crowded. One try and I‚Äôm hooked.

Tried their curry fish head for the first time. Piping hot and Overall taste is good. Their ingredients quite generous as per pic. Fish no smelly smell. Can call to order then pick up in order to minimise waiting time.
